  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0d85\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dbb\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u2019\u2019 306\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "306 were caught from the \"guest's night\".",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Office of the Superintendent of Police states that 306 people were arrested for various offenses in the \"Visitor's Night\" operation conducted by the 19 police stations belonging to the Gampaha Police Division.",
        "In this six-hour night operation, 86 evading warrants, 20 for possession of heroin and cannabis, 28 for possession of illegal alcohol and 51 suspects were arrested.",
        "Also, four drivers for driving under the influence of alcohol, four people for driving without a driver's license, one for careless driving and 113 people for other traffic offenses have been arrested in this operation."
      ],
